mail-notification: mail-notification (tray icon)
mail-notification:
mail-notification: Mail Notification is a status icon (aka tray icon)
mail-notification: that informs you if you have new mail.
mail-notification: 
mail-notification: It works with system trays implementing the
mail-notification: freedesktop.org System Tray Specification, such as the
mail-notification: GNOME Panel Notification Area, the Xfce Notification
mail-notification: Area and the KDE System Tray.
